{"tid":904761,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"屌21歲以下嘅囡囡屎眼原來要坐成世監","createTime":"2018-11-16T15:21:34.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-17T03:24:49.000Z","uid":95684,"like":1,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"70b3ba576c1c37dd8c1d8b0afed709035e2fc359","tid":904761,"uid":95684,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:21:34.000Z","msg":"第200章 《刑事罪行條例》 第118D條 與21歲以下女童作出肛交<br />\n<br />\n任何男子與年齡在21歲以下的女童作出肛交，即屬犯罪，一經循公訴程序定罪，可處終身監禁<br />\n。(由1991年第90號第3條增補)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"312820c8522fe927ec0dadc4f68cf0485e17f923","tid":904761,"uid":26506,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:28:12.000Z","msg":"今年司法覆核同性罪行贏咗，法律改革委員會前幾年都建議過"},{"pid":"bd3a3a48bc867f6f12514bc1478d7c7ce9eda94c","tid":904761,"uid":61271,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:31:18.000Z","msg":"高等法院早在2005年裁定，《刑事罪行條例》中有21歲以下男性同性肛交屬違法的條文，是違憲和無效。2014年同性肛交的合法年齡已正式由21歲改至16歲。不過《刑事罪行條例》至今仍然定明，任何男子與21歲以下女士肛交屬犯罪，最高刑罰是終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n法改會的諮詢文件認為，性罪行的法律不應帶有性傾向或性行為習慣方面的區分，因此提出建議，在香港同意年齡應劃一為16歲，不論性別和性傾向而適用。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/society/法改會倡合法性交年齡劃一16歲-擬廢除異性肛交21歲限制/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%83%E5%80%A1%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B4%E9%BD%A1%E5%8A%83%E4%B8%8016%E6%AD%B2-%E6%93%AC%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E7%95%B0%E6%80%A7%E8%82%9B%E4%BA%A421%E6%AD%B2%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%2F&d=QtGvvLdS3H5QvTHz1eNTE7%2BHiWCy6q6AsXO%2BLNmzhis%3D&h=f16b1bf9\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fsociety%2F%E6%B3%95%E6%94%B9%E6%9C%83%E5%80%A1%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%A4%E5%B9%B4%E9%BD%A1%E5%8A%83%E4%B8%8016%E6%AD%B2-%E6%93%AC%E5%BB%A2%E9%99%A4%E7%95%B0%E6%80%A7%E8%82%9B%E4%BA%A421%E6%AD%B2%E9%99%90%E5%88%B6%2F&h=1cf61a10\" target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/society/法改會倡合法性交年齡劃一16歲-擬廢除異性肛交21歲限制/</a>"},{"pid":"c6586d6a1bc8926a5cb1b6f875318f8e2167d0b0","tid":904761,"uid":67908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T15:56:23.000Z","msg":"咁男童呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c89cae019b1883927d5ef0b85e3978a18c8c7d1d","tid":904761,"uid":191296,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:02:24.000Z","msg":"想知點解<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4cf26ff9bca1fd89b854a0efba19581102a33a0d","tid":904761,"uid":26451,"like":14,"dislike":1,"score":13,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:11:45.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"baaf2d1b2b3543ca44b2507cd985404d8a2ffcf2","tid":904761,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"點解21歲都係童<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a77dfe7c157c892ac4760ae83dd018eba640c76e","tid":904761,"uid":7206,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"baaf2d1b2b3543ca44b2507cd985404d8a2ffcf2","tid":904761,"uid":6030,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T16:16:05.000Z","msg":"點解21歲都係童<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-16T17:43:01.000Z","msg":"有啲新聞啲女成3張野都叫少女啦，21歲係童真係唔出奇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7786bc733c9c3a7e29b98633aaa1275771ceee2a","tid":904761,"uid":95684,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-17T02:30:21.000Z","msg":"一定有好多大學生係hall犯法，點捉佢地好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/999.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dbe4a3ac9